# Assets Directory

This directory contains static assets like images, icons, and other media files.

## Required Files:
- favicon.ico - Website favicon
- apple-touch-icon.png - iOS home screen icon (180x180px)
- og-image.png - Open Graph image for social sharing (1200x630px)

## Recommended Sizes:
- favicon.ico: 32x32px (with 16x16px fallback)
- apple-touch-icon.png: 180x180px
- og-image.png: 1200x630px

## File Formats:
- Use WebP for images when possible for better compression
- Include PNG fallbacks for broader compatibility
- SVG for icons and simple graphics

## Optimization:
- Compress all images before deployment
- Use appropriate file formats for each use case
- Consider lazy loading for non-critical images